author: Kristina Wong, Kristina Wong
title: Pompeo on Possibility of Wuhan Lab Leak: 'Still Lots to Find Out'
description: Pompeo did not rule out the possibility of a coronavirus leak from a virology lab in Wuhan, China, in a radio interview on Tuesday.
content:
Secretary of State Mike Pompeo did not rule out the possibility of a coronavirus leak from a virology lab in Wuhan, China, in a radio interview on Tuesday.
